  "elements": [
    {
      "id": "J6389cV3tAmjHO5_uX0RG",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3452.392857142857,
      "y": 2358.6666666666665,
      "width": 815.4593505859375,
      "height": 1200,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a0",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2063983404,
      "version": 1637,
      "versionNonce": 2128491156,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1784566873660,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Instagram/FB Feed\n\nRequirements -> Core Entities -> APIs -> HLD -> Deep Dives\n\nFunctional Requirements\n1. User should be able to register and login\n2. User should be able to follow other users\n3. User should be able to create posts\n4. User should be able to view posts by other followed users\n5. User should be able to react or comment on posts\n\nNon Functional Requirements\n1. Eventual Consistency -> created posts should be visible in feed in about 1 minute\n2. High Throughput -> Consider 500 M concurrent users minimum\n3. Low Latency -> feed should be scrollable and should be visible under 500 ms\n4. High Availability and Fault Tolerant\n\nCore Entities\nUsers\nFollowers\nPosts\nComments\nReactions\n\nAPIs\n\nRegister/Login\nPOST /registration\nPOST /login/ -> {userId}\n\nFollow\nPOST /followers -> {userId, followedUserId}\n\nCreate Post\nPOST /user/{userId}/posts\nGet Post Feed\nGET /user/{userId}/posts?cursor=&limit=\n\nGET Comments\nGET /posts/{postId}/comments?cursor=&limit=\nPost Comments\nPOST /posts/{postId}/comments\n\n\nGet Reactions\nGET /posts/{postId}/reactions/?cursor=&limit=\nPOST Reactions\nPOST /posts/{postId}/reactions",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Instagram/FB Feed\n\nRequirements -> Core Entities -> APIs -> HLD -> Deep Dives\n\nFunctional Requirements\n1. User should be able to register and login\n2. User should be able to follow other users\n3. User should be able to create posts\n4. User should be able to view posts by other followed users\n5. User should be able to react or comment on posts\n\nNon Functional Requirements\n1. Eventual Consistency -> created posts should be visible in feed in about 1 minute\n2. High Throughput -> Consider 500 M concurrent users minimum\n3. Low Latency -> feed should be scrollable and should be visible under 500 ms\n4. High Availability and Fault Tolerant\n\nCore Entities\nUsers\nFollowers\nPosts\nComments\nReactions\n\nAPIs\n\nRegister/Login\nPOST /registration\nPOST /login/ -> {userId}\n\nFollow\nPOST /followers -> {userId, followedUserId}\n\nCreate Post\nPOST /user/{userId}/posts\nGet Post Feed\nGET /user/{userId}/posts?cursor=&limit=\n\nGET Comments\nGET /posts/{postId}/comments?cursor=&limit=\nPost Comments\nPOST /posts/{postId}/comments\n\n\nGet Reactions\nGET /posts/{postId}/reactions/?cursor=&limit=\nPOST Reactions\nPOST /posts/{postId}/reactions",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
